                                                Clerk's Office Hours

                                                      Flag Line
                              The Office of the Clerk (in both divisions) is open from
                                        8:30 a.m. until 4:30 p.m. on all days
                                    except Saturdays, Sundays and legal holidays.
                               After hours emergency filings should be directed to the
                                                  Bankruptcy Clerk.
